---
name: leadbay_research_a_domain
kind: prompt
short_description: |
  Import a company by domain and run deep qualification + research in one
  pass. Use when a colleague mentions a name and you want everything Leadbay
  knows about it.
arguments:
  - name: domain
    description: "The company's primary domain (e.g. 'acme.com'). Protocol/path are stripped."
    required: true
expected_calls:
  - leadbay_import_and_qualify
  - leadbay_research_lead
failure_modes:
  - Fabricates qualification answers not present in any tool response
